{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303530/extras/CnR_ManandaHorse_ss.gif?t=1726141463\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>A man and a horse walk into a saloon\u2026</i></strong></h2><br>Experience the story of two outlaw friends - an overly joyful rustler and a talking, cynical horse - told through the magic of a top-down action video game. Rob banks and roller-coasters summon ghosts at cemeteries, all while helping your horse friend in writing his revolutionary science-fiction novel.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303530/extras/CnR_WeirdWest_s.gif?t=1726141463\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>Kinda Wild, Somewhat Weird West</i></strong></h2><br>That\u2019s what the outsiders call it, interchangeably with Kinda Wild, Boy Do They Smell There West. It\u2019s full of cowboys, skater(cow)boys, dusty towns, and photovoltaics. Everyone is weirdly enamored with spitting into spittoons and their favorite soup is whisky. Yet there\u2019s also beauty. Some have honest work and don\u2019t overwater their cactuses. There are even people with hobbies besides not starving to death.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303530/extras/CnR_UniversalTools_s.gif?t=1726141463\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>Universal tools of communication</i></strong></h2><br>In a place as kinda wild and somewhat weird, it\u2019s good to know how to communicate. Revolvers usually make the most convincing argument, especially with the help of swift fingers and good use of ricochet physics. A few lasso tricks and a Gatling gun will be irreplaceable in more complex discussions. It\u2019s also worth remembering that nothing\u2019s more powerful than friendship and a kick of a 1000-pound horse.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303530/pag